<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1120</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wéi dú nǐ míng wèi yé hé huá, shì quán de yǐ shàng de zhì gāo zhě.
 nǐ bì zuò yǐ sè liè de jiān gù tái, nǐ de chǎn yè bì yǎng wàng nǐ.
 suī rán chóu dí yī tóng shāng yì, yào jiǎn miè nǐ de ér nǚ.
 dàn nǐ yé hé huá shì wǒ men de shén, bì tì wǒ men zhēng zhàn.
 yuàn chóu dí yǒng yuǎn xiū kuì jīng huāng, yuàn chóu dí sù sù miè wáng.
 jīn rì quán de dōu zài chuán yáng, yé hé huá wèi yǐ sè liè xíng dà shì.</lyrics>
<title>wéi dú nǐ de míng wèi yé hé huá 迦南1120</title>
</song>